\begin_layout Section
HTTP
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
What is HTTP
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Puntos a tratar: what HTTP is and basic features, when it was created and
 its creator, versions, basic architecture, how it work.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
placement H
